1554
02:53:43,680 --> 02:53:45,600
"I'm on my way," I replied.

1555
02:53:47,120 --> 02:53:52,319
Jose was looking much brighter. 
His head was heavily bandaged,  

1556
02:53:52,319 --> 02:53:58,160
but he was sitting up in bed. "Nat, 
