1557
02:53:58,880 --> 02:54:05,840
"what happened on that night out. I can 
remember things now - places, people, faces."

1558
02:54:07,439 --> 02:54:12,879
Piece by piece, Jose put the story 
together. Everything matched what  

1559
02:54:12,880 --> 02:54:19,920
I already knew until he reached the point 
where he'd made a grab for the baseball bat.

1560
02:54:19,920 --> 02:54:28,160
"OK, now Jose, take it slowly from this point," 
I said. "Tell me everything you saw or heard."

1561
02:54:29,359 --> 02:54:37,040
"I looked up and saw this crowd standing 
over me. Wow! They were mad as hell at me.  

1562
02:54:38,160 --> 02:54:44,720
I couldn't understand what I'd done. Then I 
realized it was something to do with the bat.  

1563
02:54:45,760 --> 02:54:49,200
I heard someone shouting 
'What the hell are you doing?'  

1564
02:54:50,240 --> 02:54:57,599
I was lying there, scared, surrounded by a 
bunch of real angry guys. Then someone pushed  

1565
02:54:57,600 --> 02:55:03,040
through the crowd and said: 'Don't touch 
him. He's mine. I'll take care of him'."

1566
02:55:04,160 --> 02:55:06,080
"What did he look like?" I asked.

1567
02:55:06,800 --> 02:55:14,000
"A big, tough guy, as tall as Joe here," 
said Jose. "He was wearing a shiny suit.  

1568
02:55:14,640 --> 02:55:21,920
