a face like a boxer who's lost too many fights."

1569
02:55:23,200 --> 02:55:27,439
"Sounds exactly like our 
friend Zernov. Go on, Jose."

1570
02:55:28,479 --> 02:55:33,679
"He picked me up off the floor. This 
guy's name, you said it was Zernov?  

1571
02:55:34,399 --> 02:55:38,240
Well he was holding my arm 
behind my back with a tight grip.  

1572
02:55:39,120 --> 02:55:45,200
Then he spoke again to the crowd, and repeated: 
'I'll take care of him. Got any objections?"'

1573
02:55:46,399 --> 02:55:48,479
"Then he bought you a drink?" I asked.

1574
02:55:49,200 --> 02:55:57,279
