03:03:44,479 --> 03:03:50,399
Jose was named as having been arrested and 
charged with the murder of Alexei Romanov.

1648
03:03:51,680 --> 03:03:57,440
Perfect. The publicity would, 
hopefully, deceive Zernov and Mossolov.  

1649
03:03:58,560 --> 03:04:02,560
As long as they were acting 
under a false sense of security,  

1650
03:04:02,560 --> 03:04:07,920
they might proceed with bringing 
in the next shipment of immigrants.

1651
03:04:07,920 --> 03:04:12,560
