1655
03:04:37,600 --> 03:04:43,440
Now assuming the shipment will be landed 
on Fire Island, then it should be a simple  

1656
03:04:43,439 --> 03:04:52,080
surveillance operation to follow any vehicle to 
its destination. That's where we should strike. I  

1657
03:04:52,080 --> 03:04:57,359
