risk of hanging around exposed beaches."

1658
03:04:58,720 --> 03:05:01,920
"All seems logical enough to me," said Lockhart.

1659
03:05:03,040 --> 03:05:09,519
"Now we already know that Mossolov Import and 
Export is located on Brighton Beach Avenue.  

1660
03:05:10,479 --> 03:05:17,200
I don't believe the immigrants will be taken 
there. It'd be too obvious. I know from Boris  

1661
03:05:17,200 --> 03:05:22,399
Tchernov's statements that the immigrants 
were taken to some sort of factory building  

1662
03:05:22,399 --> 03:05:29,359
