at sea observing any movements there. Also,  

1667
03:05:58,720 --> 03:06:03,360
a Coast Guard helicopter from Air 
Station Cape Cod would be on patrol  

1668
03:06:04,080 --> 03:06:09,439
and Coast Guard officers would be posted 
along Fire Island at regular intervals.  

1669
03:06:10,720 --> 03:06:16,560
The police part of the operation was to observe 
all road exit points from the beaches to the  

1670
03:06:16,560 --> 03:06:23,121
