most of the information in this case so far?"

1676
03:06:55,520 --> 03:06:57,360
"Yes," replied Oldenberg.

1677
03:06:58,399 --> 03:07:03,599
"And you know my personal interest 
in this case. I want to prove,  

1678
03:07:03,600 --> 03:07:11,840
without any doubt, that De La Cruz is innocent. 
And also, I want to find out who killed Romanov.  

1679
03:07:12,800 --> 03:07:17,840
I need a confession. That's why we 
have to be there at the finish."

1680
03:07:18,960 --> 03:07:25,840
"You're both ex-NYPD, so you're well aware 
of the risks," said Oldenberg bluntly.  

1681
03:07:26,800 --> 03:07:33,360
