about playing the hero, Marley. Understood?  

1682
03:07:34,319 --> 03:07:41,200
We'll have all units in position by dusk, and I'll 
keep in regular contact with you by cell phone."

1683
03:07:42,800 --> 03:07:45,840
Joe and I had little else to do until nightfall.  

1684
03:07:46,800 --> 03:07:52,320
Before leaving for Coney Island, I put a 
call through to Stella to give her an update.

1685
03:07:53,200 --> 03:08:01,120
