1690
03:08:21,279 --> 03:08:26,639
Another call to Mrs. Romanov to inform 
her of the real purpose of the bulletins  

1691
03:08:27,200 --> 03:08:30,800
and to reassure her that we 
were making definite progress.

1692
03:08:32,080 --> 03:08:38,640
"I'm reasonably optimistic that your husband's 
killer will be behind bars by tomorrow," I said.

1693
03:08:40,000 --> 03:08:44,479
"Take care, Mr. Marley and 
God be with you," she replied.

1694
03:08:45,840 --> 03:08:52,560
We headed off in the rental car towards the 
Brooklyn Bridge. Through the steel network I  

