1696
03:08:59,120 --> 03:09:04,800
reflecting off the surface. We passed 
rapidly through the suburbs of Brooklyn  

1697
03:09:04,800 --> 03:09:11,200
on Ocean Parkway, which eventually brought us 
onto Surf Avenue, parallel to the oceanfront.

1698
03:09:12,640 --> 03:09:20,240
We had some time to kill, so I asked Joe to 
continue west along Surf Avenue. The amusement  

1699
